  <body>
    <segment id="1">

One man&apos;s joy ... 
</segment>
    <segment id="13" parent="19" relname="interpretation">

The threat was not carried out.
</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="3" relname="antithesis"> 

In August of this year, at a residents&apos; meeting, the anger of the people of Kloster was vented in the announcement that the construction of the new federal highway and the Jüterbog bypass would be stopped.
</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="19" relname="span">  

But since yesterday, construction machinery has been digging into the ground on the eastern edge of Jüterbog.
</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="17" relname="circumstance">  

The route has been marked out,
</segment>
    <segment id="14" parent="15" relname="antithesis"> 

and it does not go around the monastery,
</segment>
    <segment id="15" parent="17" relname="span"> 

but rather directly into the town.
</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="21" relname="span">

So it&apos;s clear that yesterday&apos;s ground-breaking ceremony was not all happy faces and good words.
</segment>
    <segment id="6" parent="16" relname="antithesis">  

And not only among the people from the Kloster Zinna citizens&apos; initiative who were present,
</segment>
    <segment id="16" parent="22" relname="span"> 

but also, for example, Jüterbog&apos;s champion for traffic calming in the town center and Schloßstraße.
</segment>
    <segment id="7" parent="26" relname="span">  

Hildegard Uebe took the opportunity to have a serious word in person with the head of the Wünsdorf road construction office about the problems that remain despite the bypass.
</segment>
    <segment id="8" parent="24" relname="interpretation">

This did not dampen the euphoric mood.
</segment>
    <segment id="9" parent="23" relname="span">  

Rather cheerfully, Minister Meyer once again put the Klosterans off until the next Federal Transport Infrastructure Plan.
</segment>
    <segment id="10" parent="9" relname="elaboration">  

othing would be in it before 2006.
</segment>
    <segment id="11" parent="23" relname="result">  

The faces of the Kloster residents were rather sweet and sour.
</segment>
    <segment id="12" parent="27" relname="summary">  

One man&apos;s joy is another man&apos;s sorrow.

</segment>
